    <item>
      <title>22.07.2020 [!] - Big update</title>
      <pubDate>Sun, 10 Jan 2021 23:33:45 +0000</pubDate>
      <link>https://legendware.pw/threads/22-07-2020-big-update.1104/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">1104</guid>
      <author>invalid@example.com (LegendwareAdmin)</author>
      <category domain="https://legendware.pw/forums/forum-updates/"><![CDATA[Updates]]></category>
      <dc:creator>LegendwareAdmin</dc:creator>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div class="bbWrapper">Welcome! Today we added our currency - &quot;<b>Legend coins</b>&quot;. To check your wallet you can press on new icon, on right-side from alerts <img src="https://legendware.pw/attachments/1595431680771-png.3182/"
			class="bbImage "
			style=""
			alt="1595431680771.png"
			title="1595431680771.png"
			width="107" height="41" loading="lazy" /><br />
You can buy other&#039;s product for coins - [charge=0] product [/charge]<br />
<code class="bbCodeInline">[charge=100] your product or smth [/charge]</code> where 100 - price.<br />
<br />
Also, you can pay for &#039;Legend&#039; upgrade by coins. 1 rub - 0.5 coins <img src="https://legendware.pw/attachments/1595431868045-png.3185/"
			class="bbImage "
			style=""
			alt="1595431868045.png"
			title="1595431868045.png"
			width="775" height="158" loading="lazy" /><br />
<br />
There are several ways to earn them:<br />
<ul>
<li data-xf-list-type="ul">Post message - <i><b>2 coins</b></i><br />
Your message will approve <b><span style="color: rgb(235, 107, 86)">moderator</span></b>, after that you will...</li>
</ul><br />
<a href="https://legendware.pw/threads/22-07-2020-big-update.1104/" class="link link--internal">Read more</a></div>]]></content:encoded>
      <slash:comments>89</slash:comments>
    </item>
